{"tid":1919941,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"只貼靚聲碟","createTime":"2020-03-11T06:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T05:43:19.000Z","uid":201299,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"34a944b63622a9b298005b1e6da87d559c440f43","tid":1919941,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T06:27:07.000Z","msg":"論靚聲CD，陳百強嘅碟一定榜上有名，事關1985年發深愛着你頭版一碟曾被評為香港十大最靚聲CD之首，喺拍賣網更一度被炒到二萬港紙一隻。小弟冇耳福，未能一聽Sony首版嘅天籟之音，喺度只能分享音色最為接近，由馬來西亞音響雜誌《影音風雲》發行嘅版本。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i0dtpqf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi0dtpqf.jpg&h=12f6a4aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此碟音色清脆俐落，高頻響亮，低頻紮實而不會過火，層次分明，乍聽深愛着你及盼望的緣分二曲，毫無逆耳之感。陳百強於戀愛預告一曲的精彩演譯亦屬前無古人，後無來者。我和你、傷心人及在這孤獨晚上三曲動態盡現，加上敲擊樂器畫龍點睛，唯一美中不足之處是空間感較窄。臨尾兩首side track如果沒有你及永不改變，樂器密度較低，沒有過多點綴，混音拿捏得恰到好處，不會聽得沉悶。<br />\n<br />\n對比起我手上90年代T113、雙層SACD、ADMS及DSD版本，大馬版較能還原當初首版Sony 11+++++ CD的音色，久聽不厭。<br />\n<br />\n唔知你哋又有咩靚聲CD介紹呢？"},{"pid":"dbdc6369e139c3498e4d59cccb99078f634517f3","tid":1919941,"uid":201299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:56:08.000Z","msg":"Elvis with the Royal Philharmonic Orchestra - The Wonder of You<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZzTJdF6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZzTJdF6.jpg&h=1d951b19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻碟係用貓王近半世紀前嘅錄音，配上新嘅管弦樂團編曲穿越古今結合而成。與其話係貓王精選碟，不如話佢係新出嘅大碟。新編曲做到忠於原創，但聽落又有幾分清新。<br />\n<br />\n其實Royal Philharmonic Orchestra已經唔係第一次咁樣玩，呢隻之前有If I Can Dream一碟，後續有Christmas with Elvis，仲有用其他舊歌手嘅歌重新編曲出碟，例如Buddy Holly，Aretha Franklin，The Carpenters，The Beach Boys同埋Roy Orbison，有機會再分享。<br />\n<br />\n第一條track A Big Hunk o' Love係我覺得全碟最過癮嘅一曲。由精彩嘅前奏開始，低頻潛得夠深，質感豐富，咁大棚嘢夾埋絲毫不亂。碟中有好幾首貓王首本名曲，料不到嘅係改編得充滿驚喜。<br />\n<br />\n整碟嘅混音較傾向流行曲多過發燒碟/管弘，迎合大眾口味，人聲較出，層次豐富，低頻實在，值得一聽再聽。"},{"pid":"6d593721b6f4f70a61d27cf275a48acc86174bff","tid":1919941,"uid":42440,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T11:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZD0C3Yd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZD0C3Yd.jpg&h=8fa1775e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35b93e77beeda1224ad74621af512aed5ba37201","tid":1919941,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T11:46:39.000Z","msg":"強帖留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d2bbde7cd4579d557acf6a54bc42308d4851a6","tid":1919941,"uid":42440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T11:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ydusGLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FydusGLE.jpg&h=2159aa40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04839a6ab39954b9c189d59439662ece746d1ed","tid":1919941,"uid":70977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T11:54:34.000Z","msg":"Stronk post lm"},{"pid":"43467a1f4797beaa2f80f3447fb009f6906a7c57","tid":1919941,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T02:39:17.000Z","msg":"Linda Ronstadt - Duets<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBzkm91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBzkm91.jpg&h=ad6b1048&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻碟係Linda Ronstadt呢十年嘅碟入面賣得最好嗰隻，事關佢喺2012年嗰陣證實患上柏金遜病，佢嘅歌聲就此遺留喺歷史中。<br />\n<br />\n全碟嘅歌曲都係Linda Ronstadt同其他歌手嘅合唱歌，由70年代到00年代都有，但係就咁聽完全唔會覺得音色上有明顯分別，盡顯碟內曲目錄音質素，只有同Frank Sinatra合唱一曲Moonlight in Vermont中，Frank Sinatra嘅錄音密度較低，畢竟係1958年嘅錄音。"},{"pid":"e545db1e8ff62141b13cd69a4f27939f5dcab38d","tid":1919941,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21d2bbde7cd4579d557acf6a54bc42308d4851a6","tid":1919941,"uid":42440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T11:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ydusGLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FydusGLE.jpg&h=2159aa40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T02:43:22.000Z","msg":"印象中好似有出黑膠版本？應該最靚聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f77fb5de57aa780eef5e144f39eeaa32dbed74a","tid":1919941,"uid":7332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T02:52:14.000Z","msg":"留名受教"},{"pid":"c8161b23aacb72ac40d61f8d461d3f396baa93b8","tid":1919941,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:30:54.000Z","msg":"Ernest Ansermet - The Royal Ballet Gala Performances<br />\n2013 Blue Moon Producciones Discogr&aacute;ficas reissue<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NzJRKDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNzJRKDM.jpg&h=f20d4e1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻雙碟套裝簡直係「靚聲」嘅代名詞。<br />\n<br />\n1957年嘅錄音，由Ernest Ansermet擔任Royal Opera House Orchestra嘅樂團指揮，由Kenneth Wilkinson於馳名靚聲嘅London's Kingsway Hall錄音。<br />\n<br />\n當年推出嘅Living Stereo首版黑膠已經被炒至天價，連其後推出嘅24K CD都被炒至萬幾銀港紙一隻，到2013年先有一個價格較平民化嘅版本。<br />\n<br />\n此碟音場密度高，立體感十足，音色亮麗，令人聞歌起舞，簡直唔敢相信係1957年嘅錄音！<br />\n<br />\n必買！"},{"pid":"7b75e7da4c5b46049878f2941363b5f6f36cc67a","tid":1919941,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T05:43:19.000Z","msg":"羅文25 SACD<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qT3V80d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqT3V80d.jpg&h=19e5e4c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n羅文喺1996年為咗慶祝自己入行25周年出咗《羅文25》嘅CD版本，當中大部分曲目都係羅文翻唱自己經重新編曲嘅經典歌曲。當時有分3CD豪華版同2CD普通版，聲音已經不俗。2002年翻出嘅呢隻hybrid 2SACD版本早排俾人炒到2000銀一隻<br />\n<br />\n此碟SACD層錄音質素甚高，聲音十分飽滿，層次分明，樂器線條清晰，聽出耳油"}]}